        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个子图结构。客户端层我理解为工厂现场的设备，服务器层是云端或数据中心，那Vite这层是做什么的？是消息队列还是网关聚合？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Vite",
        "P1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Vite这层是遥测数据流的汇聚点，P1节点负责收集多个PLC的数据并统一转发。客户端层我准备放四个节点：C1、C2、C3是三个PLC逻辑控制器，C4是执行器控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "P1",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Cliente子图已创建，包含C1、C2、C3三个PLC逻辑节点和C4执行器控制器。Vite子图包含P1遥测流节点。现在服务器层需要哪些节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "P1",
        "Cliente",
        "Vite"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务器层需要S1和S3两个PLC逻辑节点做协议转换，S2做遥测流处理，S4是执行器控制器，最重要的是S5边缘节点，它是整个服务器层的核心调度中心。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5",
        "Servidor",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Servidor子图已添加五个节点。现在来连接数据流：C1到C2是现场级联，然后到P1汇聚，P1再连到S1进入服务器层，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "P1",
        "S1"
